  "uuid": "a898dd9f4921c4aaaecd017fda88f5d9",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Spa Therapist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<p>* Perform professional facials and other beauty services for customers</p>\n<p>* Create a safe space for your clients to disclose their face concerns, taking note of their individual needs, routines, and goals</p>\n<p>* Ensure each client receives an extraordinary treatment for their individual needs and goals.</p>\n<p>* Provide a friendly, compassionate environment, deep product/protocol knowledge and honest advice</p>\n<p>* Educate clients on both the protocol being administered as well as their own unique skincare concerns and questions by modelling our innovative philosophy</p>\n<p>* Handle administrative duties, manage appointments, maintaining client records, inventory and operating supplies</p>\n<p>* To perform any other ad-hoc duties as assigned by superiors.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>* Willing to learn, truly passionate about skincare &amp; beauty and making clients happy and beautiful inside and out, self-motivated and able to work in international, fast paced environment</p>\n<p>* Must be highly professional and very detail oriented. The person(s) we are seeking must have an interest in the health and wellness field.</p>\n<p>* Partial experience at beauty salon/spa with a proven track record of excellence in aesthetic.</p>\n<p>* Build rapport with customers</p>\n<p>* Provide customers with professional massage service.</p>\n<p>* Follow up on customers after-experience</p>\n<p>* Great communicating skills</p>\n<p>* Able to work as a team and individually.</p>\n<p>* Positive attitudes</p>\n<p>* Customer oriented</p>\n<p>* Target driven</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>职位描述：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>提供全面的面部护理服务。</li>\n  <li>深入了解客户的皮肤需求与目标，制定个性化护理计划，确保每位客户获得专业和周到的护理。</li>\n  <li>在愉悦的环境中为客户提供美容服务，让他们感受到放松与关怀。</li>\n  <li>提供专业建议，向客户解释每项护理流程，帮助他们理解护肤效果和过程。</li>\n  <li>处理行政事务，包括管理预约、客户记录、库存管理等，确保日常运营顺利。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>要求：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>拥有美容师资格证或相关美容专业经验。</li>\n  <li>精通面部护理、按摩等美容服务，能够根据客户需求提供个性化的服务方案。</li>\n  <li>出色的沟通技巧，能够清晰地解释护肤流程，理解客户需求，建立信任关系。</li>\n  <li>高度专业，注重细节，积极学习，乐于帮助客户实现他们的美容目标。</li>\n  <li>有团队合作精神，并能独立完成工作，具备强烈的目标导向。</li>\n  <li>具备良好的客户服务意识，能够通过提供卓越的服务赢得客户的信任和忠诚。</li>\n  <li>能够在快速变化的国际化工作环境中自我激励，并适应多变的工作需求。</li>\n</ul>",
